WEBVTT

1
00:11:00.220 --> 00:11:02.548 
你比我拉的大多数乘客年轻。
You're younger than most of my passengers.

2
00:11:03.700 --> 00:11:05.982 
你拉很多人去疗养院吗？
Do a lot of driving for the sanitarium?

3
00:11:06.040 --> 00:11:07.426 
都是我拉。
All the driving.

4
00:11:07.500 --> 00:11:09.997 
每个星期我都会拉上下了火车的有钱人，
Every week, I pick up rich people from the train...

5
00:11:10.020 --> 00:11:11.769 
把他们送上山。
and take them up the mountain.

6
00:11:11.920 --> 00:11:13.922 
只是有钱人，哈？
Only rich people, huh?

7
00:11:14.080 --> 00:11:15.809 
那上面一定贵得很。
Must be expensive.

8
00:11:15.860 --> 00:11:18.461 
是啊，富人有富人的问题。
Well, wealthy people have wealthy problems.

9
00:11:18.520 --> 00:11:20.622 
对我来说，我很满意简单的生活。
Me, I'm happy with a simple life.

10
00:11:20.680 --> 00:11:22.802 
就这样了？没有其他奢望？
That's it? No ambition?

11
00:11:22.840 --> 00:11:25.198 
只想开车送人上山下山？
Just drive people up and down the mountain?

12
00:11:26.620 --> 00:11:28.504 
大多数人会留下来。
Most people tend to stay.

13
00:11:28.600 --> 00:11:29.747 
为什么会这样？
Why's that?

14
00:11:30.020 --> 00:11:32.185 
我想他们喜欢那儿。
I guess they like it there.

15
00:11:32.240 --> 00:11:33.241 
噢，靠！
Oh, shit.

